\ulnone\b0\i0\fs20 This program modifies "falloutw.exe" in memory for the purposes of increasing the visual resolution. \par
It was compiled with "Visual C++ 6.0 -sp6" and should work on most versions of Windows.\par
\par
Currently Supported versions of the "Falloutw.exe" are:\par
   US 1.1.\par
   The EXE used in TeamX's English 1.2 (this executable is the same used in their fallout 1.3.4 patch) .\par
   The EXE used in the Fallout Restoration Mod by Wasteland Ghost/TeamX.\par
   Polish 1.2/TeamX.\par
   Fallout Collection (PC DVD) WHITE LABEL 1.2.\par
   Some other versions will also work but will be \cf1 recognised \cf0 as one of the versions listed above. \par
