\par
\pard\nowidctlpar\fi-360\li360\ulnone\i0\fs20 Step 1.\tab\i Extract to Fallout Directory\i0\par
\pard\nowidctlpar\li360\b0 Double-click the "Fallout1_High_Resolution_Patch_v2.2a.exe". Click the [Browse] button and find your Fallout installation folder (usually "C:\\Program Files\\Interplay\\Fallout\\"). Click [Extract], the extraction window will disappear once complete.\ul\i\fs18\par
