\par
\i0\fs20 Fallout is not starting after setting the resolution via the in-game menu.\ulnone\b0\par
Open the "f1_res.ini" found in your Fallout Install folder and return SCR_WIDTH, SCR_HEIGHT and COLOUR_BITS to their default values:\par
SCR_WIDTH=640\par
SCR_HEIGHT=480\par
COLOUR_BITS=8\par
Re-start the game and try a different resolution.\par
\par
\par
\ul\b There is no 'SCRN' button on the Game Preferences Window.\par
\b0\i\fs18 Note:\ulnone  The 'SCRN' button will only be present when accessed via the Main-menu\cf2 .\par
\i0\fs20\par
