\par
If you are using an older version of Windows (pre XP), you may need to find the run-time components for Visual C++ 6.0. These can be downloaded from Microsoft, just search for "Vcredist.exe" in your favourite search-engine.\par
\ul\i\fs18 Note\ulnone : This problem should only affect older versions of Windows. WindowsXP and Vista should already have the necessary \i0\fs20 components \i\fs18 installed.\i0\fs20\par
\par
