\tab Instructions:\par
\tab 1. Right-Click your "falloutw.exe" and select \ul Properties\ulnone . \par
\tab 2. Click the \ul Compatibility\ulnone  Tab.\par
\tab 3. Check the box next to "Run this program in compatibility mode for:"\par
\tab 4. Select \ul Windows 95\ulnone  from the drop down list below.\par
\tab 5. Click Apply.\par
